<br>
Should I look first for jewelry for stat boosts? Look for AC? Etc.<br>
<br>
Also, keeping in mind my lack of funds, should I avoid a trade like jewelry crafting, through which I would think I could get some minor items like that, but I believe the supplies/materials are pretty pricey?<br>
<br>
