<br>
The bazaar is the key to get started quick -- try to gather up 100pp first - you can try spider silks, or the earing camp mentioned above, theres also an orc drop in EC (pickbringers coif?) that sells for quite a few plat for a very low level.<br>
Once you have 100pp head on up to the bazaar and start scoping out great deals.<br>
Examples:<br>
Found a jacinth for sale for 100pp ... sells to vendor for 190pp<br>
Found a copy of Blessed Armor of the Rissen for 100pp ... sells for 1500 - 1900<br>
Acrylia ore also sells really well and people sometimes put it up for cheap prices<br>
Check gems and player made jewlery...people in bidding wars often drop their price lower than the vendor price without realizing it.<br>
<br>
Good Luck! <br>
